\f2\fs32 \cf0 Purpose:
\f0\b0 \uc0\u8232 Restore agency through felt sense, without formal instruction.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f11\fs28 \cf0 \cb5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \cb2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf9 Before anything needs to be solved, the body needs to feel included.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf9 \cb2 A small shift in attention can change the entire experience.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 Not by force, but by invitation.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf9 \cb2 Notice your breathing.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 Not the idea of breath, but the actual movement.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 Where does it arrive?\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 Where does it leave?\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf9 \cb2 You may feel sensation before understanding.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 Warmth.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 Pressure.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 A softening or a subtle resistance.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf9 \cb2 This is the body re-entering the conversation.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 It does not require belief.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 Only presence.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf9 \cb2 From here, change does not come from effort.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 It comes from cooperation.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf9 \cb2 The system responds when it senses safety.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf9 \cb2 That safety can begin with something this simple.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

